result.name: WinZip
result.u_software_restriction: As per CHG0083722, This SCR is to deploy a package to uninstall WinZip from 2000 SEC Workstations and to deploy 7-Zip to all SEC Workstations.   WinZip 17.5 is end of life and the SEC does not have the ability to upgrade to the latest version for free.  Upgrading to the non-vulnerable version of WinZip would cost $20,000.  EUT worked with OCIE, and it was agreed that WinZip could be retired and replaced with 7-Zip, which is free.  Both packages have been tested by PPE and 7-Zip is already on the ASL.
